headline: Why The Narrative Around Travelers Companies (TRV) Is Shifting After Fresh Street And Valuation Updates
summary: The latest update to Travelers Companies' fair value estimate edges the price target to roughly US$301.10 per share, even as the revenue growth assumption in the model shifts to a much more cautious 53.83% decline. That combination reflects how recent Street research is balancing confidence in the business with a tougher backdrop for pricing across parts of the P&C market.
